g.text: Sequence Diagram US236: Edit Show Request
Asks to edit a show request
Asks for the Show Request ID to edit
Displays current details (from showRequestToEdit) and asks for new data
Enters updated details (newDescription, newPlace, newDate, newDuration, newDrones)
"Do you want to change the customer? (y/n)"
Shows list of customers for selection
editShowRequest(showRequestToEdit, newDescription, newDate, newDuration, newPlace, newDrones, newSelectedCustomer)
editShowRequest(showRequestToEdit, newDescription, newDate, newDuration, newPlace, newDrones, showRequestToEdit.getCustomer())
Displays Success message and updated details
